{"tid":2257308,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"喀布爾教育中心引爆炸彈　至少18死57傷","createTime":"2020-10-25T04:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T05:03:24.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"620ff62ccfc00c40f25c4d6d3e83ebdeb57d3792","tid":2257308,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"阿富汗首都喀布爾第13警區的一個教育中心上周六（24日）遭遇自殺式爆炸襲擊，導致至少18人死亡，另有57人受傷，死者包括兒童。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">塔利班組織已否認發動襲擊，而極端組織「伊斯蘭國」聲稱對襲擊承認責任</span></strong>。阿富汗內政部指，一名男子想進入教育中心，但遭保安人員截查，他於是當場引爆炸彈。一名目擊者指，他當時站在100米以外，爆炸的衝擊力令他跌在地上。<br />\n<br />\n儘管塔利班及阿富汗政府年初於卡塔爾簽署和平協議，但近數周阿富汗的暴力事件數字卻有增無減。"},{"pid":"486ec715826e616dda9b2ad1f80aedcf2c5cdd56","tid":2257308,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556528-20201025.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556528-20201025.htm&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PQ%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=bb9285b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556528-20201025.htm&h=6f1becc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556528-20201025.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7a68f19cadc2669d24a88aa5800202d2d80250ef","tid":2257308,"uid":275692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"只少肯承認責任 好過香港班恐怖分子"},{"pid":"5249a8483ed7bcb9b57bd5ae7a0f33527d31aab6","tid":2257308,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a68f19cadc2669d24a88aa5800202d2d80250ef","tid":2257308,"uid":275692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"只少肯承認責任 好過香港班恐怖分子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:03:24.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭國無論係唔係佢都會認左先，因為要爭取曝光率"}]}